article.description: — Alex Williams' 31 points led Furman past Bob Jones 100-58 on Saturday.
article.headline: Williams scores 31, Furman downs Bob Jones 100-58
article.linkText: Williams scores 31, Furman downs Bob Jones 100-58
article.story: GREENVILLE, S.C. -- — Alex Williams' 31 points led Furman past Bob Jones 100-58 on Saturday. Williams added eight rebounds for the Paladins (5-5). JP Pegues scored 21 points and added 12 assists and four steals. Pjay Smith Jr. was 6 of 15 shooting (5 for 14 from 3-point range) to finish with 18 points. The Bruins (1-6) were led in scoring by Devin Pope, who finished with 16 points and two steals. Kenney Garrick added 11 points for Bob Jones. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
